#HTML & CSS
1.-	html color picker for color selection
2.-	border: limit of the content
	margin: distance from the border to the outside(external)
	padding: distance from the border to the content(internal)
3.-	id: used to change one thing
	class: used to modify a bunch of things

#Bootstrap
1.- https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/components/alerts/

#Sass
1.- variables
	a) use of variable in a css stylesheet (sass variables.scss variables.css)
	b) constantly update website according to the scss file (sass --watch variables.scss:variables.css)
2.- nesting
